ch.ethz.inf.vs.persistingservice.parser
Class PayloadParser

java.lang.Object
  ch.ethz.inf.vs.persistingservice.parser.PayloadParser

public class PayloadParser
extends java.lang.Object

The Class PayloadParser is used to parse the payload read from the coap requests.

It manages a hashmap of the payload labels and provides some useful methods to access the structured payload.
